        <num>27-1519</num>
        <heading>Pilot projects</heading>
        <content>
          <p>ยง 27-1519. Pilot projects.\n  The commissioner shall cooperate with the commissioner of health to\ndevelop pilot projects pursuant to subdivision 3 of section 1389-dd of\nthe public health law to promote the safe handling, treatment and\ndisposal of medical waste generated in private residences. The\ncommissioner may exempt these pilot projects from the permitting\nrequirements of this article.\n</p>
